OL,5, A scheme offering interest-free loans  
OL,6, to the financially vulnerable is being 
OL,7, expanded to reach up to 20,000 people. 
OL,9,FAfter a successful trial in Manchester 
OL,10,Fthe No Interest Loan Scheme (NILS) will
OL,11,Fbe rolled out across the UK from       
OL,12,FSeptember.                             
OL,14,FIt's backed by the Treasury but will be
OL,15,Frun by credit unions and other lenders.
OL,17,FThe aim is to offer emergency loans to 
OL,18,Fpeople who would normally be turned    
OL,19,Fdown, because they can't afford the    
OL,20,Finterest payments.                     
